source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SEQ_00<tab>N'tanmo needs help keeping the city a bright and cheery place.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SEQ_00<tab>ブルワークホールの双子の案内係ン・タンモは、都市の安全のために、依頼したいことがあるようだ。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SEQ_01<tab>Unable to leave her post, N'tanmo has tasked you with inspecting the streetlamps about town. Refill them with streetlamp oil lest they run dry.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SEQ_01<tab>ブルワークホールにて、都市を訪れた人々を見守る双子の案内係ン・タンモから、ランプの給油を依頼された。「油の減った街灯」に「街灯用の油」を注そう。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SEQ_02<tab>You have refilled all of the guttering streetlamps. Speak with Sisipu at the Fishermen's Guild to receive more streetlamp oil.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SEQ_02<tab>「油の減った街灯」への給油を終えた。漁師ギルドの「シシプ」に、街灯用の油の配達を依頼しよう。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SEQ_03<tab>You learn that N'tanmo has a habit of foisting her duties upon fledgling adventurers, much to Sisipu's disapproval. However, you sense that there is more to Sisipu's frustrations than meets the eye.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SEQ_03<tab>漁師ギルドの「シシプ」に、油の配達を依頼した。シシプは、仕事を冒険者に押し付ける案内係ン・タンモにお冠だ。しかし、その怒りの原因は、どうやら責任感の問題だけではないようだ。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_TODO_00<tab>Refill guttering streetlamps with streetlamp oil.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_TODO_00<tab>油の減った街灯に街灯用の油を注ぐ

source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_TODO_01<tab>Speak with Sisipu at the Fishermen's Guild.

TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_NTANMO_000_0Sounds like you're already in the Yellowjackets' good graces. You truly are a model adventurer─a paragon among your fellows!
...Um, do you think you could do me a favor?
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_NTANMO_000_0早速、イエロージャケットから、
ご指名受けちゃうなんて、さすがですね。
ついでに、私のお願いを聞いてもらえません？

source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_NTANMO_000_1<tab>You see, I'm supposed to go and fill up all the streetlamps with oil so that they'll stay lit through the night. But thanks to this business of missing people, I can't simply up and leave my post.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_NTANMO_000_1ランプの手入れの時間なんですけど、
あなたが届けてくれたイエロージャケットの
お達しのせいで、私もしばらく、ここを動けません。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_NTANMO_000_2<tab>If you could tend to the streetlamps in my stead, I'd be <var 1A 02 /var>eternally<var 1A 01 /var> grateful.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_NTANMO_000_2私の代わりに、この「街灯用の油」を
街のなかの「油の減った街灯」に注いでほしいのです。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_NTANMO_000_3<tab>Oh, and when you're finished, please fetch more oil from Sisipu in the Fishermen's Guild. We're running low here, and she has care of our stores.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_NTANMO_000_3油が切れたら、「漁師ギルド」へ行って、
「シシプ」さんに油の配達をお願いしてください。
彼女が、街灯の管理もしているので。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SISIPU_000_10<tab>...You're doing <var 1A 02 /var>what<var 1A 01 /var>!? <sigh> What am I to do with that girl?
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SISIPU_000_10えっ、あなたがランプに給油してくれたの！？
あの娘ったら、また冒険者に仕事をおしつけて……

source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SISIPU_000_11<tab>She has the nerve to ask me for work, twaddlin' tripe about her savings, only to foist it on the first adventurer that comes along!
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SISIPU_000_11そもそも、小遣い稼ぎのために仕事をくれと
頼みこんできたのは、彼女の方なのに。
彼女へ油を届けたついでに、注意もしておきますね。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SISIPU_000_12<tab>Being young and pretty does <var 1A 02 /var>not<var 1A 01 /var> give you license to shirk responsibility! Aye, she'll get her oil all right...and a piece of my mind to boot!
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA010_00120_SISIPU_000_12少しばかり若くてかわいいからって、
仕事の責任を投げだすのは見逃せないわ！
